          )
        .ms-image-link__overlay
        .ms-image-link__content
          h2.ms-image-link__title Ready to Move to the Cloud?
          p.ms-image-link__description
            | Schedule a free consultation with our cloud architects. Let's design the
            | infrastructure your business deserves.
          span.ms-image-link__cta Book a Free Consultation
